                <solution>
                    <p><md>
                    <mrow>\fe{\fd{k}}{x}&amp;=\frac{2(x-4)\cdot(x+3)-(x-4)^2\cdot1}{(x+3)^2}</mrow>
                    <mrow>&amp;=\frac{2x^2-2x-24-(x^2-8x+16)}{(x+3)^2}</mrow>
